18.description: We are an Agent of Change that offers Online Educational Experiences and training to children, youth and adults under the approach of Science, Technology, Society + Innovation, with the methodology of "Learning by Doing & Playing" which allows to put into practice all the knowledge acquired by developing entertaining technological projects. We have an online platform where we offer the services of E-Learning courses (recorded), live courses (Online Robotics & Technology Academy), Sales of Robotics Kits and Events for Institutions/Communities. We also offer the Learning Route, a total of 12 specialized courses through which the child is guided from the most basic knowledge to the realization of various projects set in the most demanded skills of the XXI century (Programming, Robotics, Electronics, Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, Design and 3D Printing, Innovation and Entrepreneurship).  We also offer teacher training and consulting for schools in the implementation of innovative educational methodologies. Within our online platform, we sell different products and tools to the Community. It also allows to upload different e-learning courses generated by us and also by a network of external educators, includes a learning community where we form groups for our live online classes (Online Robotics & Technology Academy service), the classes are recorded, so participants can access all the educational content complementing the learning with tutorials and projects sections, includes a gamification system where we encourage to participate and interact with different users, achieving badges, levels and points that can be used as discounts for different products and services. Our scalability is sustained by being able to reach the largest number of people around the world through our online tool and our network of educators that allows us to impact this new model to different communities that want to learn 21st century skills and digital languages from an early age.
